<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">وك أ:</span> <span class="c2">(الْمُتَّكَأُ)</span> مَوْضِعُ <span class="c2">(الِاتِّكَاءِ)</span> وَفَسَّرَهُ الْأَخْفَشُ فِي الْآيَةِ بِالْمَجْلِسِ. <span class="c2">(وَتَوَكَّأَ)</span> عَلَى الْعَصَا. وَ <span class="c2">(أَوْكَأَهُ إِيكَاءً)</span> أَيْ نَصَبَ لَهُ مُتَّكًا.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وِكَافٌ فِي أك ف وَفِي<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>